All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
ArtifactUtil
The ArtifactUtil class contains methods to help with the management of artifacts.
CacheCorruptedException
The CacheCorruptedException class is used to throw an exception when the cache is corrupted.
MavenArtifact
The MavenArtifact class represents a maven artifact on the Maven Central Repository.
MavenArtifactBean
The MavenArtifactBean class is used to represent a maven artifact.
MavenArtifactCache
The MavenArtifactCache class is used to cache artifacts to avoid making multiple requests to the maven repository for the same artifact.
MavenArtifactType
The MavenArtifactType enum is used to represent the different types of artifacts.
MavenCache
The MavenCache class implements both the MavenSearchCache and the MavenArtifactCache classes.
MavenSearchBean
The MavenSearchBean class is used to represent a maven search.
MavenSearchCache
The MavenSearchCache class is used to cache search results to avoid making multiple requests to the maven repository for the same search.
MavenVersionBean
The MavenVersionBean class is used to represent a maven artifact version.
SearchCacheEntryBean
The SearchCacheEntryBean class is used to represent a search cache entry.
